Pa, zar to nije dobro?
Bie sigurnija, zar ne?

244
00:33:49,780 --> 00:33:50,620
Misli?

245
00:33:50,740 --> 00:33:51,420
Da.

246
00:33:52,180 --> 00:33:53,980
Izvini, ali dovoljno je loe
to treba da ivimo

247
00:33:54,100 --> 00:33:56,940
preko puta ulice u odnosu
na njegovog oca posle tog...

248
00:33:57,020 --> 00:33:59,700
incidenta, od ranije.

249
00:34:00,620 --> 00:34:03,340
Frank, on je ba uvrnut.

250
00:34:03,420 --> 00:34:04,660
A da li si primetio i novu suprugu?

251
00:34:04,780 --> 00:34:06,220
Stalno je viam u trnom centru,

252
00:34:06,300 --> 00:34:08,340
uvek je u toj prodavnici, 
gledajui...

253
00:34:08,420 --> 00:34:09,780
Ne znam...

254
00:34:09,900 --> 00:34:12,860
bilo bi previe pristojno
koristiti re "zajedniko".

255
00:34:12,980 --> 00:34:14,500
I deak je ba udan.

256
00:34:14,580 --> 00:34:17,500
Stalno se unja okolo sa svojom kamerom,

257
00:34:17,620 --> 00:34:20,780
pijunira kao neki mali perverznjak.

258
00:34:20,860 --> 00:34:22,820
Neu tako.

259
00:34:25,460 --> 00:34:27,980
Hoe li da nabavi brave?

260
00:34:30,060 --> 00:34:31,020
iveli.

261
00:35:23,180 --> 00:35:24,820
Ove nam nita ne govore.

262
00:35:24,940 --> 00:35:26,500
ta?!

263
00:35:27,860 --> 00:35:31,060
Pa...,
ta je sa kadom?

264
00:35:31,140 --> 00:35:32,300
Ovo je previe oigledno.

265
00:35:32,380 --> 00:35:34,420
Mislim, ubice nee razdvojiti delove tela

266
00:35:34,540 --> 00:35:36,500
u svom dvoritu, zar ne?

267
00:35:36,580 --> 00:35:39,740
Osim toga, to su mrave devojke.
Nema mesa na njima.

268
00:35:39,860 --> 00:35:43,940
Pa, osim moda kod Terese.
Imala je veliko dupe i male sise.

269
00:35:45,540 --> 00:35:47,140
Ovo je samo poetak toga, Danny.

270
00:35:47,220 --> 00:35:50,460
Nisi jo ak ni zagrebao povrinu.

271
00:35:54,020 --> 00:35:57,740
ovo je ga Howatt,
Amandina majka.

272
00:35:57,860 --> 00:36:01,740
Ona e ekati dok se pakao ne smrzne.

273
00:36:05,100 --> 00:36:07,300
ne mogu da verujem da sam je
pre samo 4 dana nazvala kukom.

274
00:36:09,060 --> 00:36:12,020
Kuka danas, a nestala sutradan.

275
00:36:13,380 --> 00:36:16,100
Ovo je porodica Dispina.

276
00:36:17,100 --> 00:36:20,060
Najstarija erka, Sofia,
mi je prole godine rekla

277
00:36:20,180 --> 00:36:23,060
da otac nee da ih ostavi na miru...

278
00:36:23,180 --> 00:36:25,740
ako zna na ta mislim.

279
00:36:32,500 --> 00:36:36,460
Ovo je najvea misterija u ulici.

280
00:36:39,860 --> 00:36:43,380
Zato stoji tamo po ceo dan?

281
00:36:46,420 --> 00:36:49,060
Odgovori na pitanja
lee u toj kui, Danny.

282
00:36:49,140 --> 00:36:53,700
Ti i ja emo otkriti sve njene tajne.

283
00:36:55,540 --> 00:36:57,660
A kad to i uradimo...

284
00:36:58,780 --> 00:37:02,340
uhvatiemo i ubicu.

285
00:37:05,940 --> 00:37:08,300
Imam mali test za tebe, Danny.

286
00:37:11,540 --> 00:37:14,140
Veeras, kada padne mrak,

287
00:37:14,260 --> 00:37:18,060
hou da se uunja u neke od tih kua...

288
00:37:18,140 --> 00:37:20,580
da ih slika...

289
00:37:20,660 --> 00:37:23,820
i da mi otkrije neke tajne.

290
00:38:49,540 --> 00:38:51,260
Suzy!

291
00:38:51,380 --> 00:38:52,860
Da li zna ta radi?

292
00:38:53,940 --> 00:38:55,740
Lii! ga! Voli ga!
Sisaj ga! Kurac!

293
00:38:55,860 --> 00:38:57,860
Na ta lii?

294
00:38:57,940 --> 00:38:59,460
Duo, samo se... pogledaj.

295
00:38:59,540 --> 00:39:01,500
Paradira po kui, praktino gola

296
00:39:01,620 --> 00:39:02,700
a zavese nisu navuene!

297
00:39:02,780 --> 00:39:03,940
Pa?

298
00:39:04,020 --> 00:39:06,620
Pa, ljudi gledaju!

299
00:39:06,740 --> 00:39:08,420
Duo, oni gledaju!

300
00:39:08,500 --> 00:39:10,260
Tako bi mogla da poalje pozivnicu

301
00:39:10,340 --> 00:39:11,980
svakom perverznjaku u susedstvu!

302
00:39:12,060 --> 00:39:14,660
Sredi se, majko!

303
00:39:18,220 --> 00:39:20,180
Da zna...

304
00:39:20,260 --> 00:39:22,660
Kad bi samo znala.

305
00:39:42,980 --> 00:39:44,500
Namerno si to uradio.

306
00:39:44,660 --> 00:39:45,340
Nisam.

307
00:39:45,460 --> 00:39:48,420
Jesi. Gledala sam te.

308
00:39:49,420 --> 00:39:51,420
Pa, mogu li da dobijem nazad svoju loptu?

309
00:39:54,660 --> 00:39:56,220
Ne.

310
00:39:58,580 --> 00:40:00,980
Ko si ti uopte?

311
00:40:03,500 --> 00:40:05,780
Nema veze ko sam ja.

312
00:40:05,860 --> 00:40:09,860
Samo hou da me ostavi na miru.
Molim te?

313
00:40:10,580 --> 00:40:12,140
ao mi je.

314
00:40:12,220 --> 00:40:14,340
Moete da zadrite loptu.

315
00:40:19,380 --> 00:40:21,620
Ko si ti?

316
00:40:23,100 --> 00:40:25,300
Ja sam Daniel.

317
00:40:25,420 --> 00:40:28,020
Daniel Hobson.

318
00:40:28,100 --> 00:40:31,700
ivim na drugom kraju ulice.

319
00:40:35,780 --> 00:40:38,940
Hm... kako se vi zovete?

320
00:40:39,740 --> 00:40:42,660
Ja sam Jennifer.

321
00:40:45,540 --> 00:40:48,180
Zdravo, Jennifer.

322
00:40:48,260 --> 00:40:50,980
Zdravo, Danny.

323
00:40:55,700 --> 00:40:58,340
Trebalo bi da se vratim unutra.

324
00:40:58,420 --> 00:41:00,180
Zdravo.

325
00:41:14,660 --> 00:41:18,140
Sada, kada si video kako izgledam,

326
00:41:18,260 --> 00:41:21,420
hoe li, molim te,
da me ostavi na miru?

327
00:42:15,220 --> 00:42:16,940
Ohh.

328
00:42:35,540 --> 00:42:37,580
Alan.

329
00:42:37,660 --> 00:42:40,020
Treba da razgovaramo.

330
00:42:40,140 --> 00:42:43,500
O emu treba da razgovaramo?

331
00:42:43,580 --> 00:42:45,100
O nama.

332
00:42:46,380 --> 00:42:48,340
Dannyju.

333
00:42:57,300 --> 00:42:59,900
Koliko god hoe da ovo izbegne,

334
00:43:00,020 --> 00:43:01,740
koliko god hoe da sakrije od prolosti,

335
00:43:01,820 --> 00:43:03,260
mi na kraju moramo da priamo o tome.

336
00:43:03,380 --> 00:43:05,100
Ako to ne uradimo,
to e nas razdvojiti u suzama,

337
00:43:05,180 --> 00:43:07,460
ukljuujui i Dannyja.

338
00:43:09,340 --> 00:43:11,780
Nita ne utie na Dannyja.

339
00:43:13,620 --> 00:43:14,620
On je samo klinac.

340
00:43:14,740 --> 00:43:15,780
To je sranje.

341
00:43:15,860 --> 00:43:17,540
Nita od ovoga nije dobro za njega, Alan...
nita od ovoga.

342
00:43:17,620 --> 00:43:20,380
Dolazim kui svakog popodneva
da bih ga nala u sobi

343
00:43:20,500 --> 00:43:24,500
kako trai neto to nije ovde.

344
00:43:24,620 --> 00:43:27,100
Daniel je moj sin.

345
00:43:27,220 --> 00:43:29,580
Ok? On je moj.

346
00:43:31,020 --> 00:43:33,180
I kao svog sina,
podizau ga kako mislim da treba.

347
00:43:33,300 --> 00:43:35,020
U tome jako grei.

348
00:43:35,100 --> 00:43:37,380
Ti jako grei,
i jako si okrutna.

349
00:43:37,460 --> 00:43:39,700
Daniel je na sin.

350
00:43:39,820 --> 00:43:41,740
On je na!

351
00:43:43,300 --> 00:43:44,940
Voleo bih da tako razmiljam
posle 14 godina,

352
00:43:45,020 --> 00:43:47,100
ja sam malo vie od devojke
koja ivi sa vama, zna,

353
00:43:47,220 --> 00:43:48,620
ja sam Dannyju malo vie od maehe.

354
00:43:48,700 --> 00:43:50,740
Ja sam sve to to je ikada poznavao.

355
00:43:52,500 --> 00:43:55,540
Alan, nain na koji krije tajne od njega,

356
00:43:55,620 --> 00:43:57,540
nain na koji razgovara sa njim...

357
00:43:57,620 --> 00:44:02,300
njegov nedostatak identiteta,
napravio je drutvenog izgnanika od njega.

358
00:44:02,420 --> 00:44:05,700
On je klinac koji nema vezu 
sa stvarnim svetom.

359
00:44:05,780 --> 00:44:08,420
Sad je dosta. Ok?

360
00:44:08,500 --> 00:44:10,540
Dosta.

361
00:44:12,820 --> 00:44:18,140
Sada bi trebalo da uuti
pre nego to ode predaleko, Sherrie.

362
00:44:18,260 --> 00:44:19,940
Ok?

363
00:44:22,340 --> 00:44:23,660
On je 14-togodinjak,

364
00:44:23,780 --> 00:44:27,980
koji nikad nije video sliku
svoje prave majke.

365
00:44:28,100 --> 00:44:30,780
Boga mu, Alan.

366
00:44:40,180 --> 00:44:42,500
Kako se zvala?

367
00:44:44,180 --> 00:44:46,660
Moe li da mi kae?

368
00:44:47,540 --> 00:44:50,260
Moe li da mi kae to?

369
00:44:53,620 --> 00:45:01,740
ta joj se desilo?

370
00:45:11,740 --> 00:45:13,820
ta si joj ti uradio?

371
00:45:14,420 --> 00:45:16,620
ta si uradio?

372
00:45:42,420 --> 00:45:44,100
Sada...

373
00:45:44,900 --> 00:45:46,580
Priaj sa mnom.

374
00:45:46,700 --> 00:45:49,020
Pa, ta je to to tako brzo
hoe da mi kae?

375
00:45:49,980 --> 00:45:51,780
Video sam je.

376
00:45:51,860 --> 00:45:53,900
enu iz broja 46.

377
00:45:54,020 --> 00:45:55,580
Video sam kako izgleda.

378
00:45:57,540 --> 00:45:59,060
Suzy?

379
00:45:59,220 --> 00:46:01,460
Hoe li Daniel ostati na veeri?

380
00:46:03,020 --> 00:46:04,860
Ne, u redu je.

381
00:46:04,980 --> 00:46:07,380
ta, uopte, imamo?

382
00:46:07,500 --> 00:46:09,100
Tvoje omiljeno... lazanju.

383
00:46:09,180 --> 00:46:11,620
Pa, nadam se da je vegetarijanska, majko.

384
00:46:11,700 --> 00:46:14,900
Izvini, od kada si vegetarijanac?

385
00:46:15,060 --> 00:46:17,100
Od kada sam na televiziji,
pre par dana,

386
00:46:17,180 --> 00:46:19,700
gledala dokumentarac o klanju ivotinja.

387
00:46:19,780 --> 00:46:22,820
To je odvratno. Meso je ubistvo.

388
00:46:22,940 --> 00:46:25,100
Pa, vegetarijanac ili ne,

389
00:46:25,180 --> 00:46:27,940
veera je na stolu za pola sata.

390
00:46:33,300 --> 00:46:34,540
I?

391
00:46:35,340 --> 00:46:37,900
Bila je fina.

392
00:46:38,940 --> 00:46:42,340
Bila je, nekako, udna, ali fina.

393
00:46:42,500 --> 00:46:44,260
udna?

394
00:46:44,980 --> 00:46:47,020
U kom smislu?

395
00:46:47,100 --> 00:46:49,460
Bila je psiho ili ta?

396
00:46:51,060 --> 00:46:53,740
Ne, ne ba.

397
00:46:54,420 --> 00:46:58,340
Izgledala je uplaeno.

398
00:46:58,420 --> 00:46:59,820
Izala je na vrata,

399
00:46:59,900 --> 00:47:03,500
i izgledala je kao da e je
neko ili neto

400
00:47:03,620 --> 00:47:06,540
zgrabiti iznutra.

401
00:47:07,180 --> 00:47:10,300
Rekla mi je da se zove Jennifer.

402
00:47:10,420 --> 00:47:13,580
Znala sam da mora biti neto glupo,
kao Jennifer.

403
00:47:13,660 --> 00:47:15,620
ta je imala na sebi?

404
00:47:15,780 --> 00:47:17,980
Ne znam.

405
00:47:19,700 --> 00:47:21,780
Kako je to mogue?

406
00:47:21,900 --> 00:47:24,020
Bila je obuena, zar ne?

407
00:47:24,860 --> 00:47:26,900
Da, imala je odeu.

408
00:47:27,020 --> 00:47:30,180
Jednostavno, nisam obratio panju na to
ta ima na sebi.

409
00:47:30,340 --> 00:47:32,300
Da li je to to?

410
00:47:32,380 --> 00:47:34,060
Zar nema nita vie?

411
00:47:35,700 --> 00:47:40,180
Rekla je da sad,
kad sam video njeno lice,

412
00:47:40,300 --> 00:47:42,860
treba da je ostavim na miru.

413
00:47:44,740 --> 00:47:46,860
To je uvrnuto.

414
00:47:47,940 --> 00:47:51,220
Zna da to nije sve, zar ne, Danny?

415
00:47:51,340 --> 00:47:52,540
Na ta misli?

416
00:47:52,660 --> 00:47:55,380
Pa, treba da je malo upozna...

417
00:47:55,500 --> 00:47:59,460
tako da na kraju moe 
da ue u tu kuu.

418
00:48:00,740 --> 00:48:04,700
Sada hou da saznam o tom ludaku
sa kojim ivi,

419
00:48:04,900 --> 00:48:07,780
tipu, koga nikad ne viamo.

420
00:48:13,500 --> 00:48:15,500
Ali, kako to da uradim?

421
00:48:16,940 --> 00:48:17,780
Danny...

422
00:48:17,860 --> 00:48:19,980
sigurna sam da e nai nain.

423
00:48:20,060 --> 00:48:21,580
ta vie, ti si udak.

424
00:48:21,660 --> 00:48:24,220
Niko ne obraa panju na tebe.

425
00:48:36,700 --> 00:48:38,540
Danny...

426
00:48:41,300 --> 00:48:43,380
Doi ovamo na minut.

427
00:48:45,940 --> 00:48:48,300
Zato?

428
00:48:48,860 --> 00:48:51,980
Samo uradi kako ti kaem
i doi ovamo.

429
00:49:07,220 --> 00:49:10,780
Da li si ikada poljubio devojku, Danny?

430
00:49:16,660 --> 00:49:18,460
Jesam.

431
00:49:19,700 --> 00:49:21,420
Naravno da jesam.

432
00:49:31,380 --> 00:49:33,220
Nisam.

433
00:49:35,380 --> 00:49:37,540
Pa...

434
00:49:38,620 --> 00:49:41,700
za sve postoji prvi put.

435
00:49:59,100 --> 00:50:01,180
Vidi, Danny...

436
00:50:01,940 --> 00:50:04,340
znam da e pronai nain 
da ue u broj 46,

437
00:50:04,460 --> 00:50:06,740
i da e upoznati tu devojku.

438
00:50:08,820 --> 00:50:12,300
Donesi mi i njegovu sliku, takoe.

439
00:50:14,900 --> 00:50:19,900
Uzbudljivo, zar ne?

440
00:51:51,300 --> 00:51:52,980
ta to, jebeno, gleda?

441
00:51:53,100 --> 00:51:54,820
U ta to, jebeno, gleda?!

442
00:53:08,980 --> 00:53:09,780
Zato da ne?

443
00:53:09,900 --> 00:53:12,820
Zato to ima previe godina
za to eerno sranje, zato ne.

444
00:53:12,940 --> 00:53:14,860
Nai neto to i ja mogu da jedem.

445
00:53:14,940 --> 00:53:16,940
Nikad ne jede cerealije.

446
00:53:17,020 --> 00:53:20,500
Pa, ako nae neto to i ja mogu
da jedem, onda hou.

447
00:53:30,580 --> 00:53:33,060
Danny, zaboravila sam mleko.

448
00:53:33,140 --> 00:53:35,620
Moe li da ode i da ga donese?

449
00:53:37,060 --> 00:53:38,580
Molim te?

450
00:56:31,460 --> 00:56:34,540
Pa, oigledno su to neka pitanja
koja moram da postavim,

451
00:56:34,660 --> 00:56:36,140
pa uzmi vremena koliko ti treba.

452
00:56:37,300 --> 00:56:38,620
I otac...

453
00:56:38,780 --> 00:56:41,900
da li je on tvoj deko ili suprug?

454
00:56:42,020 --> 00:56:43,620
On je moj deko.

455
00:56:43,700 --> 00:56:46,660
Mi smo zajedno skoro 14 godina, 
tako da...

456
00:56:46,740 --> 00:56:50,540
Da li ste prvo razgovarali 
sa njim o tome?

457
00:56:52,220 --> 00:56:53,900
Hm...

458
00:56:55,700 --> 00:56:58,260
Doktorka, mogu li...
mogu li da budem iskrena sa Vama?

459
00:56:58,380 --> 00:57:01,820
Naravno. Molim Vas.

460
00:57:03,780 --> 00:57:05,380
Prekid te trudnoe

461
00:57:05,460 --> 00:57:08,620
ne znai da ne elim tu bebu.

462
00:57:09,380 --> 00:57:15,460
Znai da je za mene nemogue
da je imam.

463
00:57:15,540 --> 00:57:21,740
Vidite, imam sina 
koji za mene znai ceo svet.

464
00:57:21,820 --> 00:57:25,980
Stvarni razlog da ne dobijem bebu
je moja veza.

465
00:57:30,860 --> 00:57:32,180
Hm, ima skoro 14 godina.

466
00:57:32,300 --> 00:57:35,140
ivim sam sa ovekom
o kome ne znam nita.

467
00:57:35,220 --> 00:57:40,300
Mislim, ne znam ta misli ili... osea.

468
00:57:41,500 --> 00:57:44,460
Nemam pojma ko je on zaista.

469
00:57:45,380 --> 00:57:47,300
I...

470
00:57:49,100 --> 00:57:51,540
u poslednje vreme sam poela
da mislim da je...

471
00:57:52,820 --> 00:57:55,180
da bi on mogao da bude lo.

472
00:57:56,460 --> 00:57:58,540
Mogao bi da bude opasan.

473
00:58:06,220 --> 00:58:08,020
Ja...

474
00:58:10,620 --> 00:58:14,700
Odbijam da imam dete
sa ovekom koji me plai.

475
00:59:51,980 --> 00:59:52,820
Sranje, Danny!

476
00:59:53,420 --> 00:59:54,700
ta?

477
00:59:54,780 --> 00:59:57,580
Videla sam ranije ovog tipa.

478
00:59:57,660 --> 01:00:00,060
Moj otac sakuplja 
kriminalistike asopise.

479
01:00:00,140 --> 01:00:01,580
On ih voli.

480
01:00:01,660 --> 01:00:04,060
Mislim da su to, kao,
policijska obavetenja ili tako neto.

481
01:00:04,180 --> 01:00:05,780
Zar ih tvoj tata ne dobija?

482
01:00:05,940 --> 01:00:09,420
Da, ali mi nikad ne dozvoljava
da ih pogledam.

483
01:00:10,580 --> 01:00:13,020
Da, moj tata je po malo grub.

484
01:00:13,180 --> 01:00:14,500
Opsednut je njima.

485
01:00:14,580 --> 01:00:16,140
On se drui sa grupom ljudi sa posla,

486
01:00:16,220 --> 01:00:19,060
koji se pale na tu vrstu stvari.

487
01:00:19,180 --> 01:00:21,860
Fotografije u njima su odvratne.

488
01:00:24,100 --> 01:00:26,740
Zato ih pominje?

