553
01:06:13,820 --> 01:06:16,220
Da li jo neko zna?

554
01:06:20,100 --> 01:06:21,540
Ne.

555
01:06:21,620 --> 01:06:23,500
Samo ja.

556
01:06:29,500 --> 01:06:31,580
Ok.

557
01:06:31,660 --> 01:06:33,980
Ovo mora prestati, Danny.

558
01:06:34,060 --> 01:06:36,340
Ne moe stalno da me posmatra,

559
01:06:36,460 --> 01:06:38,860
