560
01:06:38,980 --> 01:06:42,180
Ja ne treba da budem spaena.

561
01:06:44,780 --> 01:06:45,860
Danny...

562
01:06:46,780 --> 01:06:51,460
Nije sigurno da se mota
oko ulaza u ovu kuu.

563
01:06:51,540 --> 01:06:56,060
Nije sigurno da razgovara sa mnom
i da me slika.

564
01:06:57,340 --> 01:07:00,940
ovek sa kojim ivim je... bolestan.

565
01:07:02,300 --> 01:07:07,220
i ponekad, kada mu je jako loe,

566
01:07:07,340 --> 01:07:09,860
postaje opasan.

567
01:07:12,260 --> 01:07:15,340
Zna li ta mislim pod "opasan"?

568
01:07:17,100 --> 01:07:19,980
Znam tano.

569
01:07:20,580 --> 01:07:24,380
Dobro. Drago mi je da razume.

570
01:07:24,540 --> 01:07:28,180
Da li je on ubio sve one devojke?

571
01:07:32,820 --> 01:07:35,500
Ko god da ti pria te prie,

572
01:07:35,580 --> 01:07:37,740
lae te.

573
01:07:37,820 --> 01:07:39,860
Nema devojaka, Danny.

574
01:07:39,980 --> 01:07:40,740
To su lai.

575
01:07:40,900 --> 01:07:41,900
To je istina!

576
01:07:42,020 --> 01:07:44,740
Bilo ih je tri.
uo sam sve prie.

577
01:07:44,820 --> 01:07:49,900
Ljudi u susedstvu uvek izmiljaju prie.

578
01:07:49,980 --> 01:07:51,980
Ja sam odrasla sluajui prie.

579
01:07:52,100 --> 01:07:55,340
To je... urbana legenda, Danny.

580
01:07:55,460 --> 01:07:56,460
Tra.

581
01:07:56,580 --> 01:07:58,020
Ali, ta je sa Amandom?

582
01:07:58,220 --> 01:08:01,260
Devojka iz ulice, iz broja 8.
To je tano.

583
01:08:01,340 --> 01:08:05,260
Ne. Jedino to je tano je
da devojke ponekad odlaze.

584
01:08:05,420 --> 01:08:07,500
Ponekad pobegnu.

585
01:08:10,580 --> 01:08:13,540
Pa, ako ste Vi toliko nesreni 
i ako je on toliko opasan,

586
01:08:13,620 --> 01:08:15,500
zato ne pobegnete?

587
01:08:18,340 --> 01:08:21,380
Pa, prolo je vreme kada sam to radila.

588
01:08:22,740 --> 01:08:25,900
Ali problem je u tome...

589
01:08:25,980 --> 01:08:29,580
to te prolost sustigne.

590
01:08:29,700 --> 01:08:33,900
Na kraju se vrati na mesto
koje si napustio.

591
01:08:34,020 --> 01:08:36,460
Uvek se vraa.

592
01:08:36,540 --> 01:08:38,420
Uvek.

593
01:08:50,940 --> 01:08:54,540
Ima iste prste...

594
01:08:54,660 --> 01:08:57,500
iste zglobove.

595
01:09:01,580 --> 01:09:04,580
Mogu li da ti pokaem
neto stvarno posebno,

596
01:09:04,660 --> 01:09:08,940
neto to jako dugo 
nikome nisam pokazala?

597
01:09:44,580 --> 01:09:47,140
Vidi li ovo?

598
01:09:47,580 --> 01:09:50,700
Ne lii na mnogo toga?

599
01:09:51,940 --> 01:09:55,500
Ovo predstavlja mene 
pre svega ovoga...

600
01:09:56,940 --> 01:09:58,940
pre ovog ivota.

601
01:10:05,340 --> 01:10:07,540
Za mene...

602
01:10:09,580 --> 01:10:13,100
svet je bio lep.

603
01:10:16,580 --> 01:10:18,820
ali, onda... ostari...

604
01:10:24,420 --> 01:10:26,820
stvari se dese...

605
01:10:28,300 --> 01:10:31,740
i nije vie tako.

606
01:10:31,940 --> 01:10:36,460
Ne elim vie da se mota 
oko ulaza u kuu.

607
01:10:37,340 --> 01:10:40,100
Ne elim vie da me slika.

608
01:10:40,900 --> 01:10:45,900
Poni da tretira ovu kuu
kao i sve ostale u ulici...

609
01:10:45,980 --> 01:10:48,140
ignorii je.

610
01:10:50,620 --> 01:10:53,980
Ako se vrati i pronae te ovde,

611
01:10:54,060 --> 01:10:57,300
uradie neto stvarno loe,

612
01:10:59,340 --> 01:11:04,300
i onda nita vie u ivotu 
nee biti lepo.

613
01:11:08,340 --> 01:11:10,420
A sada izai.

614
01:11:11,820 --> 01:11:14,300
Hajde, izlazi!

615
01:11:15,900 --> 01:11:19,780
Neu... neu i ne treba mi tvoja pomo,

616
01:11:20,860 --> 01:11:23,420
i ne treba da me spasava.

617
01:11:25,700 --> 01:11:29,900
Izlazi!

618
01:12:32,820 --> 01:12:34,860
Ne! Ne!

619
01:12:37,140 --> 01:12:38,540
Molim te! Molim te!

620
01:12:42,420 --> 01:12:45,340
Suzy! Suzy!

621
01:12:45,420 --> 01:12:51,580
Suzy!

622
01:12:53,460 --> 01:12:55,500
Ne!

623
01:13:06,060 --> 01:13:08,300
Pitau te jo jednom, Daniel.

624
01:13:09,780 --> 01:13:12,460
Da li je bilo neeg to ste
ti i ta devojka radili,

625
01:13:12,580 --> 01:13:14,660
to nije smelo da se radi?

626
01:13:14,740 --> 01:13:15,220
Ne.

627
01:13:15,340 --> 01:13:17,420
Postoji li neto to nam
ne govori, bilo ta?

628
01:13:18,740 --> 01:13:21,020
Bolje ti je razmilja brzo, Daniel,
jer je devojka nestala.

629
01:13:21,100 --> 01:13:23,300
Ne! U redu?
Mi smo se druili,

630
01:13:23,380 --> 01:13:24,740
priali o stvarima,

631
01:13:24,820 --> 01:13:27,860
o mrtvim devojkama
i broju 46, to je sve!

632
01:13:27,980 --> 01:13:30,260
Kojim mrtvim devojkama?
ta misli pod tim, "mrtve devojke"?

633
01:13:30,380 --> 01:13:32,540
Ne znam...
one o kojima svi priaju,

634
01:13:32,620 --> 01:13:33,860
nestalim.

635
01:13:34,020 --> 01:13:37,020
To je sranje, Daniel.
To je urbani mit.

636
01:13:37,100 --> 01:13:41,260
ta jo?
ta je sa brojem 46?

637
01:13:41,380 --> 01:13:42,860
Mojim?!

638
01:13:42,980 --> 01:13:44,300
ta je sa brojem 46?!

639
01:13:44,420 --> 01:13:46,140
Ne znam, tata!

640
01:13:46,220 --> 01:13:47,980
Bolje bi ti bilo da je to sve, Daniel.

641
01:13:48,060 --> 01:13:50,220
I molim Boga da ne krije neto,

642
01:13:50,300 --> 01:13:52,620
jer, ako krije,
ivot te devojke je u opasnosti.

643
01:13:52,740 --> 01:13:54,020
Jesi li to shvatio?!

644
01:13:54,100 --> 01:13:55,500
Dosta!

645
01:13:55,620 --> 01:13:57,260
On je dete.

646
01:13:57,380 --> 01:14:02,740
Dosta je.

647
01:14:15,260 --> 01:14:18,460
Bolje da proverim tu kuu.

648
01:14:26,220 --> 01:14:27,380
U redu je.

649
01:15:14,060 --> 01:15:16,140
Zdravo, dobili ste
Alana, Sherrie, and Dannyja.

650
01:15:16,260 --> 01:15:17,820
Nismo trenutno kraj telefona,

651
01:15:17,900 --> 01:15:20,780
ostavite poruku.
Zdravo.

652
01:15:24,580 --> 01:15:26,220
Danny, jesi li tamo?!

653
01:15:31,500 --> 01:15:33,300
Suzy! Ovde sam! Suzy!

654
01:15:33,420 --> 01:15:35,180
Danny.

655
01:15:35,300 --> 01:15:39,100
Ne govori nita, ok?
Samo sluaj.

656
01:15:39,180 --> 01:15:41,260
Samo sluaj jer ako uradim 
neto pogreno,

657
01:15:41,340 --> 01:15:44,100
on e me presei na pola.

658
01:15:44,180 --> 01:15:46,140
Skloni taj no od mene, seronjo!

659
01:15:46,220 --> 01:15:47,060
Suzy! Suzy!

660
01:15:47,180 --> 01:15:48,780
Oh! To jebeno boli!

661
01:15:48,860 --> 01:15:51,500
Radim ta si traila.

662
01:15:53,580 --> 01:15:56,980
Danny, pomozi mi.

663
01:15:57,100 --> 01:16:00,380
On je besan, a ja se jako plaim.

664
01:16:00,460 --> 01:16:04,580
On zna da si poslao pandure, 
Danny, u kuu 46.

665
01:16:04,660 --> 01:16:07,340
On zna.

666
01:16:07,420 --> 01:16:10,100
Kae da treba da doe ovamo.

667
01:16:10,220 --> 01:16:15,100
Molim te, Danny.
Samo uradi kako kae, Danny, molim te.

668
01:16:17,020 --> 01:16:21,220
Danny, napustio je sobu na sekund.

669
01:16:21,300 --> 01:16:23,540
Ne dovodi nikoga, ok?

670
01:16:23,660 --> 01:16:26,380
Doi sam.

671
01:16:26,500 --> 01:16:29,540
Samo doi, ali doi veeras.

672
01:16:29,620 --> 01:16:31,180
Mora da me spase, Danny!

673
01:16:31,260 --> 01:16:32,860
Suzy! Suzy!

674
01:16:32,940 --> 01:16:33,820
Pomozi mi!

675
01:16:33,900 --> 01:16:34,740
Suzy!

676
01:18:43,860 --> 01:18:46,100
Otvori vrata!

677
01:18:47,260 --> 01:18:50,340
Ne dozvoli da na gost eka.

678
01:18:52,300 --> 01:18:55,060
Molim te, idi kui. Idi kui.

679
01:18:55,180 --> 01:18:58,460
Rekla sam ti da ne dokazi ovamo
i ti si mi obeao.

680
01:18:58,540 --> 01:19:00,380
Idi!

681
01:19:00,460 --> 01:19:02,580
Pouri!

682
01:19:04,220 --> 01:19:07,420
Ako je klinac, pusti ga unutra!

683
01:19:07,500 --> 01:19:11,260
Vreme je da on i ja
malo porazgovaramo!

684
01:19:30,100 --> 01:19:33,140
On je u sobi pozadi.

685
01:20:21,380 --> 01:20:23,660
Ulazi, deko.

686
01:20:24,660 --> 01:20:27,580
Nemam celu no.

687
01:20:52,180 --> 01:20:55,740
Jennifer mi pria
da si nam pravio probleme.

688
01:20:55,820 --> 01:20:57,980
Da li je to tano?

689
01:20:59,820 --> 01:21:01,900
Gde je ona?

690
01:21:02,020 --> 01:21:03,940
Ko?

691
01:21:04,020 --> 01:21:05,980
Suzy?

692
01:21:06,060 --> 01:21:07,820
Gde si je sakrio?

693
01:21:08,460 --> 01:21:11,220
Da li je ovo neka ala?

694
01:21:13,100 --> 01:21:15,780
Da li se ti to zajebava sa mnom?

695
01:21:17,460 --> 01:21:19,340
Da li?

696
01:21:26,980 --> 01:21:29,220
ta ti je to oko vrata?

697
01:21:34,460 --> 01:21:36,740
Foto aparat.

698
01:21:36,820 --> 01:21:41,860
Aparat.

699
01:21:43,180 --> 01:21:46,540
ta hoe da uradi tim aparatom?

700
01:21:47,660 --> 01:21:50,700
Da slikam.

701
01:21:51,820 --> 01:21:53,860
Vidi...

702
01:21:54,540 --> 01:21:58,660
