kao to si ti.

706
01:22:08,420 --> 01:22:11,780
Koji uvek misle da su bolji,

707
01:22:11,860 --> 01:22:14,060
koji me sputaju...

708
01:22:16,940 --> 01:22:19,820
unitavajui mi ivot.

709
01:22:21,300 --> 01:22:22,980
Ali tu si ti,

710
01:22:23,060 --> 01:22:29,620
