tvojim malim aparatom, hm?

711
01:22:29,740 --> 01:22:32,660
Zato Jennifer panii.

712
01:22:32,780 --> 01:22:33,780
To je ini paranoinom

713
01:22:33,900 --> 01:22:37,260
