da nastavim sa svojim ivotom.

721
01:23:17,740 --> 01:23:21,180
Ljudi kau da sam perverznjak.

722
01:23:24,140 --> 01:23:27,180
Ti si mali udak.

723
01:23:33,780 --> 01:23:35,220
Nemoj ni da pomisli da sam glup.

724
01:23:35,340 --> 01:23:37,460
Znam sve to si do sada radio.

725
01:23:37,580 --> 01:23:39,660
Viam te na ulici,

726
01:23:39,740 --> 01:23:42,180
tebe i tu malu piku.

727
01:23:42,260 --> 01:23:44,340
Kako bee njeno ime?

728
01:23:48,340 --> 01:23:50,020
Spusti ga dole, Max.

729
01:23:50,100 --> 01:23:52,300
On je... on je samo deak.

730
01:23:52,420 --> 01:23:54,660
Molim te, spusti ga dole.

731
01:23:54,820 --> 01:23:57,060
Uuti!

732
01:23:57,140 --> 01:23:58,260
On je, jebeno, zapoeo ovo,

733
01:23:58,380 --> 01:24:01,620
